WEBVTT

00:01:29.847 --> 00:01:36.847
And in the same family,
girls and boys are brought up differently.

00:01:37.167 --> 00:01:39.063
Boys are taught

00:01:39.087 --> 00:01:43.647
they must be responsible for the financial

00:01:43.647 --> 00:01:46.647
and practical well being of their parents 
and siblings,

00:01:46.647 --> 00:01:49.703
find solutions for problems,

00:01:49.727 --> 00:01:52.223
obviously find a good job.

00:01:52.247 --> 00:01:57.743
When they get married, it must be
to a girl who gels with the family,

00:01:57.767 --> 00:02:02.207
because she is not only marrying
the boy but the entire family.